properties.Name: Mine
properties.Description: A mine from which resources are extracted.

Columns.Name: MineId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a mine.

Columns.Name: MineName
Columns.Description: The name of the mine.

Columns.Name: MineDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a mine.

Columns.Name: MineFirstOperationalDate
Columns.Description: The first operational date of the mine.

Columns.Name: MineLastOperationalDate
Columns.Description: The last operational date of the mine.

Columns.Name: MineGeologyStatement
Columns.Description: A statement describing the geology of the mine.

Columns.Name: MineMetallurgyStatement
Columns.Description: A statement describing the metallurgy of the mine.

Columns.Name: MineProcessingStatement
Columns.Description: A statement describing the mine processing of the mine.

Columns.Name: MineTransportStatement
Columns.Description: A statement describing the mine transportation of the mine.

Columns.Name: MineResourceStorageStatement
Columns.Description: A statement describing the mine resource storage of the mine.

Columns.Name: WasteStorageStatement
Columns.Description: A statement describing the mine waste storage of the mine.

Columns.Name: MineLatitude
Columns.Description: The latitude of the mine.

Columns.Name: MineLongitude
Columns.Description: The longitude of the mine.

Columns.Name: MineEstimatedProvenTons
Columns.Description: The estimated proven tons of resource at the mine.

Columns.Name: MineEstimatedReserveTons
Columns.Description: The estimated reserve tons of resource at the mine.

Columns.Name: EstimatedMineLifeYears
Columns.Description: The estimated mine life in years.

Columns.Name: MineNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the mine.

Columns.Name: MineFirstExplorationDate
Columns.Description: The date of the first mine exploration.

Columns.Name: MineFirstFeasibilityStudyDate
Columns.Description: The date of the first mine feasibility study.

Columns.Name: MineDevelopmentDate
Columns.Description: The date of mine development.

Columns.Name: MinePermitsAppliedDate
Columns.Description: The date mine permits were applied for.

Columns.Name: MinePermitsReceivedDate
Columns.Description: The date mine permits were received.

Columns.Name: MineFirstProductionDate
Columns.Description: The date of mine first production.

Columns.Name: MineLastProductDate
Columns.Description: The date of mine last production.

Columns.Name: MineReclamationStartDate
Columns.Description: The date that mine reclamation started.

Columns.Name: MineReclamationEndDate
Columns.Description: The date that mine reclamation ended.

Columns.Name: MineClosureDate
Columns.Description: The date that the mine closed.

Columns.Name: GeographicAreaId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Geographic Area.

Columns.Name: PropertyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a property.

Columns.Name: MineTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a mine type.

Columns.Name: FacilityId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Facility.

Columns.Name: LocationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Location.
